'''煎餅冰'''是一种圓盤狀的[[冰|冰]]，且根據形成地的條件，直徑可由0.3公尺到3公尺不等，而厚度一般約10公分。<ref name="glos">{{Cite web|url=http://www.whoi.edu/science/PO/arcticedge/arctic_west03/facts/facts_ice.html|title=Sea Ice Glossary|work=Edge of the Arctic Shelf|publisher=Woods Hole Oceanographic Institution|access-date=2016-10-05|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126035339/https://www.whoi.edu/science/PO/arcticedge/arctic_west03/facts/facts_ice.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 煎餅冰外圍有時會形成一圈略微高起的環。這種環一般是由煎餅冰互相碰撞時，堆積的碎冰和推擠的壓力而形成；而这些環也是碎冰變成煎餅冰的第一个明顯跡象。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.antarctica.ac.uk/living_and_working/diaries/rrs_james_clark_ross/antarctic2004_2005/14_21/index.php|title=Ice work|date=March 3, 2005|work=Antarctic 2004-2005|publisher=British Antarctic Survey|accessdate=2016-10-05|archive-date=2008-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080119000624/http://www.antarctica.ac.uk/living_and_working/diaries/rrs_james_clark_ross/antarctic2004_2005/14_21/index.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>

煎餅冰被認為是當上游河水快速流下，沖刷形成的浮沫在河面角落堆積，又遇上嚴寒天氣急凍，最終導致一夜結冰所形成。大致來說，煎餅冰在寒冷地區的河流和海洋中都有可能出現。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-scotland-north-east-orkney-shetland-30530281 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2016-10-05 |archive-date=2020-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202224339/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-scotland-north-east-orkney-shetland-30530281 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

